    "http://schema.org/description": [
      {
        "@value": "<p>Quebec wrestling legend PCO makes his MEW in-ring debut! Stu Grayson\nreturns to challenge Yayne Harrison for the MEW Championship! 7 wrestlers in a\nLADDER MATCH vying for the Kingmaker&#39;s Key, giving the winner a\nchampionship match whenever they choose! &quot;The Mountain&quot; Vanessa Kraven\ndefends her MEW Women&#39;s Championship and much, much more!</p>"
